The post features an image of a letter t: Update to deposit options" that lists changes to "cash and cheque deposits at Westpac" effective from July 2020.
The claim states that Westpac: an Australian bank, will no longer accept cash or cheque deposits by the end of 2020.
The claim was found to be misleading by: who clarified that there is no change to deposits of physical cash or cheques for ordinary account holders. The image in the post relates to changes in services provided to agency banks and was cropped to exclude important explanatory information.
